{"tid":1100084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被連潑2次「熱血豆漿」！輔大女滿臉體液報案　淚求員警幫她擦拭","createTime":"2019-04-10T08:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T08:37:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1dc27d2b77313d1ace8b282553038df7b460f4","tid":1100084,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4015/d4015760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4015%2Fd4015760.jpg&h=6fc936e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手、衣、臉都是溫熱又色色的汁！<span style=\"color: red;\">新北</span>市新莊區輔大女學生在本月9日晚間，要去學校附近的健身房運動，竟在途中遭機車騎士潑灑疑似精液的液體，帶有類似漂白水的氣味令她作嘔，趕緊去派出所報案，請員警用濕紙巾幫她擦掉臉上半乾的體液。衰的是，她上個月晚上同一時間才被路過騎士潑一樣的東西！<br />\n<br />\n女大生表示，第一次被攻擊是上月18日晚上約10時45分，沒想到此次竟然也在相同的時間，而且手法一模一樣，都是騎著機車潑路過的人。<br />\n<br />\n她PO文說，「有管道的話幫我看有沒有畫面，如果有拍到我被潑，拜託讓我知道，如果有拍到車牌，如題有我的小心意請收下；真的傷心又絕望到不行了，只想要好好運動，請不要檢討被害人或模糊焦點。」另外女學生也徵求夜貓子，晚上可以載她去運動的司機，費用再另計。<br />\n有網友看到貼文後，質疑警方把體液擦掉會破壞跡證，新莊警方表示，是女大生報案後，實在無法接受有異味體液一直留在臉上，因此請警員拿紙巾擦掉，紙巾已送去檢驗，並無滅證或吃案的狀況。調閱監視器等畫面後，已鎖定犯嫌行蹤，正全力追緝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4015/d4015761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4015%2Fd4015761.jpg&h=a363367b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52ab2c1fa59a94b3ad0c77768505d7edc235de39","tid":1100084,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"街頭塗鴉"},{"pid":"fdc0b85949624e0e82381bface428d4b5f40fc53","tid":1100084,"uid":28195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實邊會feel到熱架，咪又係36.8℃？"},{"pid":"9f28e36a1d46b7c7f9a83d5649c8d7db90845a5f","tid":1100084,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"驗dna.... 精係證據"},{"pid":"fee3ea2d2e1940fb6d24ae423f39465c05c7717d","tid":1100084,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"條女幾正"},{"pid":"6086cfe652ee0445329e324443824e847510082f","tid":1100084,"uid":113379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"又係台灣<br />\n新北市+0.5分"},{"pid":"e0c9d4b8f21bb326a53155827fa4de93a1477306","tid":1100084,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f28e36a1d46b7c7f9a83d5649c8d7db90845a5f","tid":1100084,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"驗dna.... 精係證據"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:11:15.000Z","msg":"前幾晚睇法証先鋒<br />\n歐陽波比話加咗漂白水會破壞DNA"},{"pid":"8efca2f1d83dff39100fa33088879bc81912c46b","tid":1100084,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0c9d4b8f21bb326a53155827fa4de93a1477306","tid":1100084,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f28e36a1d46b7c7f9a83d5649c8d7db90845a5f","tid":1100084,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"驗dna.... 精係證據"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:11:15.000Z","msg":"前幾晚睇法証先鋒<br />\n歐陽波比話加咗漂白水會破壞DNA"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"呢位巴打好有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed68fbf535bab5c4006f493de2a5ac372c71982","tid":1100084,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdc0b85949624e0e82381bface428d4b5f40fc53","tid":1100084,"uid":28195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實邊會feel到熱架，咪又係36.8℃？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"體溫熱過皮膚表面喎<br />\n你呼氣落對手都覺得暖啦"},{"pid":"f4c71ff686d59a9872497ea476ef5c9600e6f8d9","tid":1100084,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0c9d4b8f21bb326a53155827fa4de93a1477306","tid":1100084,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f28e36a1d46b7c7f9a83d5649c8d7db90845a5f","tid":1100084,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply